Class MotionMagicWrapper

java.lang.Object
BobcatLib.Hardware.Motors.Utility.CTRE.MotionMagicWrapper
public final class MotionMagicWrapper extends Object
Immutable wrapper for configuring Motion Magic parameters on a TalonFX motor controller.
